T02TD1701E:57a-4: rig byed sgrol ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1701E:57a-5: gang zhig rmongs pas blo mdongs pa //
T02TD1701E:57a-6: rig byed sgrol ma rig pa'i mchog / rgyal po khyim bdag mgu byed pa //
T02TD1701E:57a-7: blang phyir bdag gis bri bar bya //
T02TD1701E:57a-8: gzhan yang sgrol ma'i rig pa mchog blang pa'i slad du bsnyen ba'i grangs tshad du song zhing sgrub thabs cho ga blo 'dris pa'i rten gyi gang zag gis byams pa dang snying rje sngon du bskyed la skad cig gis rig byed sgrol ma sku mdog tshos chen po lta bu zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa /
T02TD1701E:57a-9: g-yas kyi dang po mi 'jigs pa'i phyag dang /
T02TD1701E:57a-11: g-yon gyis rin po che'i gzhu dang /
T02TD1701E:57a-12: g-yon gnyis bas autpala dmar po 'dzin pa /
T02TD1701E:57a-13: rgyan sna tshogs kyis sbras pa /
T02TD1701E:57a-14: padma dang zla ba'i gdan la skyil krung gis bzhugs pa /
T02TD1701E:57a-15: de'i thugs kar pam las padma /
T02TD1701E:57a-16: aa las zla ba'i steng du t'am dmar po byi ru'i mdog lta bu las /
T02TD1701E:57a-17: phyogs bcur 'od 'phros tshur bsdus nas bdag gi kun du rmongs pa'i tshogs thams cad zhi bar bsam zhing sems gtad la bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD1701E:57a-18: de nas skye bar gyur na gsang sngags rgyun mgal me'i 'khor lo lta bus sems sbyangs nas yar ngo'i chos brgyad kyi nyin par nas mtshal dang gur gum dang gi wam rnams sbyar la padma 'dab ma bcu drug ba gnyis bris la /
T02TD1701E:57b-0: @57b aom t'a re tu tt'a re aa ni bhi pra dzny'a s'a dha na /
T02TD1701E:57b-1: aa bhi bra dzny'a pra s'a dha sv'a h'a /
T02TD1701E:57b-2: zhes bzla zhing bdag dang 'khor lo phan tshun thim zhing snying po dang gzungs dgod //
T02TD1701E:57b-3: 'khor lo gcig la dbyangs dang gsal byed bri bar bya'o //
T02TD1701E:57b-4: de nas bco lnga'i mtshan phyed la zla ba la mngon du phyogs pas mchod pa rnam pa lnga dang sbyin sreg dang gtor ma rnams phul la /
T02TD1701E:57b-5: me long g-y'a yongs su dag pa bug med pa la sindh'u ra dmar po mandala la gser ram zangs kyi thur mas 'khor lo ji lta ba bzhin du phyi nang du gnyis bris la snying po dang gzungs dang /
T02TD1701E:57b-6: phyi ma la dbyangs dang gsal byed bkod de cung zhig bzlas pa bya zhing mchod pa rnam pa lngas yang dag par mchod la 'khor lo gnyis dril te mgul du gdags par bya /
T02TD1701E:57b-7: sindhu ra legs par bsdus te dug lang ka wa ti'i sbu gur blugs la mchan khung g-yon par btags te thig le dmar po skra mtshams su bya zhing /
T02TD1701E:57b-8: bsod snyoms kyi phyir grong khyer du zhugs na rgyal po dang khyim bdag dad cing 'dun par 'gyur ro //
T02TD1701E:57b-9: sgra dang bstan bcos mang po dang //
T02TD1701E:57b-10: rol mo sgyu rtsal ji snyed dang //
T02TD1701E:57b-11: lha dang gnod sbyin bu mo sogs //
T02TD1701E:57b-12: rig byed mthu yis 'dun par byed //
T02TD1701E:57b-13: rig pa bskyed pa rdzogs so//
